column5: Made it out for the evening bite on Thursday night, action started around 4:30 and lasted till 6:25. Took 4 home, all around a pound and a half, and lost 5.  The fish were hitting lite in about 6 feet of water with scattered weeds.  Here's a pic of the happy angler with his catch, and yes I know I need a hair cut.
LOL....Great self picture!!!!  Good to see Scugog is producing some nice fish on the hard water.
I see 5 sets of eyes in there   Nice report man
Thanks for sharing eyefish.  Those wallys look yummy
good job man.  wish i could get out tomorrow.  maybe next week though ?
hair cut and a shave you bum  lol (you'll never get a girl lookin like that  lol) nice catches bro!!!
